        "subject": "LU-7988 hsm: close KUC pipe before unregistering",
        "message": "LU-7988 hsm: close KUC pipe before unregistering\n\n(COPY of LU-7992)\n\nIn llapi_hsm_copytool_unregister() close the read side of the KUC pipe\nbefore unregistering the copytool to avoid deadlocking with a ldlm_cb\nthread.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4b7962e1e5189ed828db306bf851bcbac30f53ef\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
